{"tid":750137,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韋舒亞談出「廠」：多謝艾馬利老實同我講","createTime":"2018-07-20T15:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T07:04:05.000Z","uid":161311,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b873e5df8cb5c309d8d17d3f689544cfaf54af","tid":750137,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:31:41.000Z","msg":"英格蘭中場韋舒亞今季終於離開效力了17年的阿仙奴，近日他接受訪問時表示，對新上任的領隊艾馬利充滿尊重，並感謝對方誠實地告訴他球隊已不需要他。<br />\n<br />\n26歲的韋舒亞今季以自由身形式轉投韋斯咸，近日他接受英國《鏡報》訪問時就表示，不認為是阿仙奴新領隊艾馬利把他逼走：「我對艾馬利除了尊重之外並無其他，我們曾經會面，他告訴我未來不會得到我所要求的上陣時間，我知道這是難以啟齒的事，他大可以隨便說說騙我，因此我感謝他對我如此誠實。」<br />\n韋舒亞又指自己對兵工廠仍有深厚感情，假如他在下月底作客阿仙奴的英超比賽入球的話絕對不會慶祝：「不，我做不到，阿仙奴的球迷多年來一直支持著我，我不會在他們面前慶祝。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/233128_495bd35cb5ee624fa0a1e38e003f5bb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F233128_495bd35cb5ee624fa0a1e38e003f5bb7.jpg&h=d7f7a594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180720/58462518\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F58462518&d=lNOFKpRqpTM1Ydg%2BMRg%2B6XadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=4bde09b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180720%2F58462518&h=055f6856\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20180720/58462518</a>"},{"pid":"fb2b394545f87ece3b9a20036209d7ec70fc1df3","tid":750137,"uid":161311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c77a4b5b087ffc5157b44d32d51d03f9cff7a4","tid":750137,"uid":77355,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:34:53.000Z","m